<br />An APU and a CPU are also very different beasts, but the Super NES, Jaguar, Dreamcast, PlayStation 2, and Nintendo DS all have dedicated CPUs with exclusive access to the APU. OpenCL makes PC GPUs look like CPUs. So I can see where one might get confused.

		

